    m_Localized: "Keltsk\xFD n\xE1ramek"
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 1446878900227
    m_Localized: "Mal\xFD bronzov\xFD h\xE1\u010Dek"
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 1446878900228
    m_Localized: "\u010C\xE1st sekery"
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 1446878900229
    m_Localized: "Mo\u017En\xFD bronzov\xFD ingot"
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 1446878900230
    m_Localized: "N\xE1bojnice z roku 1936"
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 1446878900231
    m_Localized: "Pu\u0161kov\xE1 n\xE1bojnice"
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 1446878900232
    m_Localized: "Zbytek brokov\xE9 n\xE1bojnice"
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 1446878900233
    m_Localized: "N\xE1bojnice do malor\xE1\u017Eky"
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 1446878900234
    m_Localized: "M\u011Bd\u011Bn\xFD krejcar"
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 1446878900235
    m_Localized: "1 koruna \u010Deskoslovensk\xE1"
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 1446878900236
    m_Localized: "Otv\xEDrac\xED o\u010Dko"
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 1446878900237
    m_Localized: "Trhac\xED z\xE1tka"
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 1446878900238
    m_Localized: "Poma\u010Dkan\xE1 hlin\xEDkov\xE1 f\xF3lie"
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 1446878900239
    m_Localized: "Olov\u011Bn\xE1 kulka"
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 1446878900240
    m_Localized: "Velk\xE1 olov\u011Bn\xE1 kulka"
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 1446878900241
    m_Localized: "P\u0159eslen"
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 1446878900242
    m_Localized: "Olov\u011Bn\xFD k\u0159\xED\u017Eek"
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 1446878900243
    m_Localized: "\u017Delezn\xE1 spona"
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 1446878900244
    m_Localized: "Kovan\xFD h\u0159eb"
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 1446878900245
    m_Localized: "Ohnut\xFD kovan\xFD h\u0159eb"
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 1446878900246
    m_Localized: "Kovan\xFD h\u0159eb"
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 1446878900247
    m_Localized: "Korunkov\xFD uz\xE1v\u011Br"
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 1446878900248
    m_Localized: "Korunkov\xFD uz\xE1v\u011Br"
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 1446878900249
    m_Localized: "Kov\xE1\u0159sk\xFD h\u0159eb"
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 1446878900250
    m_Localized: "H\u0159eb\xEDk"
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 1446878900251
    m_Localized: "Fragment h\u0159eb\xEDku"
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 1446878900252
    m_Localized: "\u010C\xE1st kapesn\xEDho no\u017Ee"
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 3871970947072
    m_Localized: "Velk\xFD keltsk\xFD zlat\xFD stat\xE9r."
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 3871970947073
    m_Localized: "1/8 zlat\xE9ho keltsk\xE9ho stat\xE9ru."
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 3871970947074
    m_Localized: "Hlin\xEDkov\xFD pam\u011Btn\xED prsten z roku 1914, pravd\u011Bpodobn\u011B
      vyroben\xFD voj\xE1kem jako upom\xEDnka na za\u010D\xE1tek prvn\xED sv\u011Btov\xE9
      v\xE1lky."
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 3871970947075
    m_Localized: "St\u0159\xEDbrn\xFD den\xE1r \u0158\xEDmsk\xE9 republiky, ra\u017Een:
      M. Atilius Saranus, 148 p\u0159. n. l., 19.5 mm, 3.8 g"
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 3871970947076
    m_Localized: "Medailon je p\u0159epracovan\xE1 st\u0159\xEDbrn\xE1 mince z roku
      1765. Na rubov\xE9 stran\u011B medailonu je vyobrazeno poprs\xED bavorsk\xE9ho
      kurfi\u0159ta Maxmili\xE1na III. Josefa Wittelsbacha (1727-1777) ."
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 3871970947077
    m_Localized: "Bronzov\xE1 so\u0161ka kance z doby lat\xE9nsk\xE9."
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 3871970947078
    m_Localized: "Jednoduch\xFD bronzov\xFD n\xE1ramek z doby kelt\u016F. Pr\u016Fm\u011Br:
      6,7 cm. Hmotnost: cca 50 g."
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 3871970947079
    m_Localized: "Bronzov\xFD h\xE1\u010Dek neur\u010Dit\xE9ho pou\u017Eit\xED z
      doby lat\xE9nsk\xE9, asi 10 cm a 70 gram\u016F."
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 3871970947080
    m_Localized: "Fragment bronzov\xE9 sekery z obdob\xED v\xEDce ne\u017E 1000 let
      p\u0159ed na\u0161\xEDm letopo\u010Dtem. V\xE1ha 235 gram\u016F."
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 3871970947081
    m_Localized: "Kompletn\xED pravd\u011Bpodobn\xFD ingot z m\u011Bd\u011Bn\xE9
      slitiny, pravd\u011Bpodobn\u011B z doby bronzov\xE9 nebo pozd\u011Bj\u0161\xED
      (2300 p\u0159. n. l. a\u017E 1500 n. l.). V\xE1ha p\u0159ibli\u017En\u011B
      46.2 gram\u016F."
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 3871970947082
    m_Localized: "Ne\xFApln\xE1 n\xE1bojnice st\u0159eliva (7,92 x 57 mm) poch\xE1zej\xEDc\xEDho
      od \u010Deskoslovensk\xE9 firmy Sellier & Bellot z roku 1936."
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 3871970947083
    m_Localized: "Munice, kter\xE1 evidentn\u011B selhala p\u0159i v\xFDst\u0159elu,
      nebo\u0165 st\u0159ela je st\xE1le sou\u010D\xE1st\xED a z\xE1palka je po\u0161kozen\xE1."
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 3871970947084
    m_Localized: "Siln\u011B po\u0161kozen\xFD zbytek n\xE1bojnice do loveck\xE9
      brokovnice."
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 3871970947085
    m_Localized: "Star\xE1 a po\u0161kozen\xE1 n\xE1bojnice do zbran\u011B mal\xE9
      r\xE1\u017Ee."
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 3871970947086
    m_Localized: "Krejcar Marie Terezie z roku 1761. Pr\u016Fm\u011Br: 25 mm. Hmotnost:
      11 gr."
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 3871970947087
    m_Localized: "Mince \u010Ceskoslovenska. Pen\u011B\u017En\xED jednotka: koruna.
      Rok vyd\xE1n\xED: 1959. Materi\xE1l: m\u011Bd\u02C7,hlin\xEDk, mangan (91+8+1).
      Okraj: \u017Eebrovan\xFD. Pr\u016Fm\u011Br: 23 mm. Hmotnost: 4 gr."
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 3871970947088
    m_Localized: "O\u010Dko z hlin\xEDkov\xE9 plechovky na n\xE1poje."
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 3871970947089
    m_Localized: "Neidentifikovateln\xE1 trhac\xED hlin\xEDkov\xE1 z\xE1tka od pivn\xED
      l\xE1hve."
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 3871970947090
    m_Localized: "Siln\u011B zdeformovan\xE1 a po\u0161kozen\xE1 hlin\xEDkov\xE1
      vani\u010Dka od pa\u0161tiky."
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 3871970947091
    m_Localized: "Kulka z perkusn\xED zbran\u011B pravd\u011Bpodobn\u011B z obdob\xED
      30ti let\xE9 v\xE1lky."
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 3871970947092
    m_Localized: "Olov\u011Bn\xE1 kulka z karabiny poch\xE1zej\xEDc\xED z 19. stolet\xED."
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 3871970947093
    m_Localized: "P\u0159eslen z olova nebo jeho slitiny, datovan\xFD nejsp\xED\u0161
      do st\u0159edov\u011Bku. M\xE1 kruhov\xFD tvar a obd\xE9ln\xEDkov\xFD pr\u016F\u0159ez.
      St\u0159edov\xFD otvor byl odlit m\xEDrn\u011B mimo st\u0159ed."
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 3871970947094
    m_Localized: "St\u0159edov\u011Bk\xFD olov\u011Bn\xFD k\u0159\xED\u017Eek pravd\u011Bpodobn\u011B
      no\u0161en\xFD na krku."
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 3871970947095
    m_Localized: "\u017Delezn\xE1 keltsk\xE1 \u0161atn\xED spona."
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 3871970947096
    m_Localized: "Kovan\xFD h\u0159eb z doby lat\xE9nsk\xE9, pravd\u011Bpodobn\u011B
      z povozu."
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 3871970947097
    m_Localized: "Dobov\u011B po\u0161kozen\xFD keltsk\xFD h\u0159eb."
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 3871970947098
    m_Localized: "Zachoval\xFD \u017Eelezn\xFD kovan\xFD h\u0159eb z doby lat\xE9nsk\xE9."
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 3871970947099
    m_Localized: "Z\xE1tka z pivn\xED lahve pivovaru \u010Cern\xE1 Hora."
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 3871970947100
    m_Localized: "Z\xE1tka pravd\u011Bpodobn\u011B z pivn\xED l\xE1hve. Bl\xED\u017Ee
      neur\u010Diteln\xE1."
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 3871970947101
    m_Localized: "Kovan\xFD h\u0159eb pro p\u0159ipev\u0148ov\xE1n\xED podkov."
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 3871970947102
    m_Localized: "Ocelov\xFD h\u0159eb\xEDk novodob\xFD."
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 3871970947103
    m_Localized: "\xDAlomek ocelov\xE9ho novodob\xE9ho h\u0159eb\xEDku."
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 3871970947104
    m_Localized: "\u017Delezn\xFD \xFAlomek pravd\u011Bpodobn\u011B zav\xEDrac\xEDho
      kapesn\xEDho no\u017Ee, na kter\xE9m byla p\u0159ipevn\u011Bna st\u0159enka."
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
